  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 34",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Arya VI</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\nthe <a href=\"/index.php/Hollow_hill\" title=\"Hollow hill\">hollow hill</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n381 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 29\">Arya V</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 33\">Samwell II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arya VI</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_35\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 35\">Catelyn IV</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_39\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 39\">Arya VII</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a> are blindfolded until they reach the <a href=\"/index.php/Hollow_hill\" title=\"Hollow hill\">hollow hill</a>, the secret base of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">forgotten fellowship</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> is brought bound before <a href=\"/index.php/Thoros_of_Myr\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thoros of Myr\">Thoros of Myr</a>, and Arya cannot believe how different the red priest looks. The Hound is to be judged by <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a> and hanged if found guilty. Thoros is a changed man, no longer a fat priest with a fake flaming sword, saying, \"I am not the false priest you knew. The <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Light\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord of Light\">Lord of Light</a> has woken in my soul. Many powers long asleep are waking, and there are forces moving in the land.\" \n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Bericdondarrion_joelhustak.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Bericdondarrion_joelhustak.jpg/300px-Bericdondarrion_joelhustak.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Bericdondarrion_joelhustak.jpg/450px-Bericdondarrion_joelhustak.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cd/Bericdondarrion_joelhustak.jpg/600px-Bericdondarrion_joelhustak.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Bericdondarrion_joelhustak.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Illustrated by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://joelhustak.deviantart.com/\">Joel Hustak</a>. © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>When Dondarrion appears, Arya is appalled by his appearance. Once handsome, the man is now stick thin, missing an eye, with part of his skull crushed in, a noose scar around his neck, and a terrible wound through his chest. Dondarrion asks for charges to be made against Sandor, but the Hound spits at the accusations, laying them at the feet of his brother and others. But Arya accuses him of killing <a href=\"/index.php/Mycah\" title=\"Mycah\">Mycah</a>, and the Hound does not refute that. The Lightning Lord sentences him to trial by battle, and it will be Dondarrion he faces. Before the fight, Thoros says a prayer to <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a>, and then Dondarrion cuts open his palm with his sword, causing the blade to take fire. \n</p><p>The fight ends with Clegane’s shield destroyed and his left arm in flames, but the Hound cuts Dondarrion from shoulder to breastbone. Sandor is screaming in pain and fear from the hideous burn to his arm. When Arya confronts him about Mycah, Clegane admits killing the boy, and suddenly Dondarrion appears, alive and leaning against Thoros, to tell Sandor he has gone to hell.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> The Hound</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Thoros_of_Myr\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thoros of Myr\">Thoros of Myr</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a> Lightning Lord</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mycah\" title=\"Mycah\">Mycah</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Greenbeard\" title=\"Greenbeard\">Greenbeard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Sevenstrings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tom Sevenstrings\">Tom Sevenstrings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mad_Huntsman\" title=\"Mad Huntsman\">Mad Huntsman</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lem\" title=\"Lem\">Lem</a> Lemoncloak</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Anguy\" title=\"Anguy\">Anguy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Edric_Dayne\" title=\"Edric Dayne\">Edric Dayne</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Hollow_hill\" title=\"Hollow hill\">Hollow hill</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">Brotherhood without banners</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Light\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord of Light\">Lord of Light</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from Aol member vbkorik27 previously at<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2013/02/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-19\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords, Part 19</a>. Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.se/2014/01/re-read-arya-vi-honor-of-dogs-and-undead.html\">Re-read Arya VI: The Honor of Dogs and the Undead</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404080049\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.073 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.294 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 242/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1104/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7916/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1258/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.37 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  268.507      1 -total\n 99.42%  266.952      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ASoS\n 99.13%  266.163      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 98.83%  265.373      1 Template:Infobox\n  0.46%    1.243      2 Template:Columns\n  0.36%    0.973      2 Template:Work_color\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5657-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404080048 and revision id 301445\n -->\n",
